ack\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mmv1665703007311.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mmv1665703007311.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mmv1665703007311.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mmv1665703007311\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $displaylength\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mmv1665703007311___displaylength_260180\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the display length of a <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> when displayed in the system character set.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__topic_d82211e1_d82212e1_d82213e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__p_d82214e1_d82215e1_d82216e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$displaylength</span> (<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vLength = $displaylength (\"The lion king”)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__topic_d54247e1_d54248e1_d54249e1_d54250e1_d54251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d191164e77\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mmv1665703007311__table_d8348e1_d8349e1_d8350e1__entry__3\">\n String, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), a variable, or a function that evaluates to a string.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__topic_d54252e1_d54253e1_d54254e1_d54255e1_d54256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d191164e131\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__p_d82223e1_d82224e1_d82225e1\">Displays the length of a string in bytes, based on\n            your system's character encoding.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__topic_d54257e1_d54258e1_d54259e1_d54260e1_d54261e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d191164e140\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__d6114e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__section_gmf_zrv_xgc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d191164e150\">Example: Using $displaylength</h2>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__example_dws_fjv_xgc\">\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example 1: UTF-8 encoding</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p\">If your system uses UTF-8 encoding, the string \"tapé\" will be measured as 5 bytes:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__ul_plk_jjv_xgc\">\n<li class=\"li\">'t', 'a', and 'p' are 1 byte each</li>\n<li class=\"li\">'é' is 2 bytes in UTF-8</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\">So, the total length is 5 bytes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example 2: Calculate string length</strong></p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mmv1665703007311_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__codeblock_xlm_njv_xgc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n   string vMyString\n   numeric vMyLength\nendvariables\nvMyString = \"Good Afternoon\"\nvMyLength = $displaylength(vMyString)\n; vMyLength will be 14 (bytes)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__example-2-field-validation\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Example 3: Use in validation</strong></p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mmv1665703007311_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mmv1665703007311__codeblock_r13_pjv_xgc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($displaylength(USER.ADDRESS) &gt; 100)\n    putmess \"Address exceeds allowed limit of 100 bytes.\"\nendif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tec1665703247413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$SYS_CHARSET</a><p>Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcg1703059864210.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>displaylength (deprecated)</a><p>Return the display length of a String when displayed in the system character set.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$displaylength Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $displaylength Return the display length of a String when displayed in the system character set. $displaylength ( String ) Example: vLength = $displaylength (\"The lion king”) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), a variable, or a function that evaluates to a string. Return Values Displays the length of a string in bytes, based on your system's character encoding. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $displaylength Example 1: UTF-8 encoding If your system uses UTF-8 encoding, the string \"tapé\" will be measured as 5 bytes: 't', 'a', and 'p' are 1 byte each 'é' is 2 bytes in UTF-8 So, the total length is 5 bytes. Example 2: Calculate string length Explain this code variables string vMyString numeric vMyLength endvariables vMyString = \"Good Afternoon\" vMyLength = $displaylength(vMyString) ; vMyLength will be 14 (bytes) Copy Example 3: Use in validation Explain this code if ($displaylength(USER.ADDRESS) > 100) putmess \"Address exceeds allowed limit of 100 bytes.\" endif Copy Related Links $SYS_CHARSET Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based. displaylength (deprecated) Return the display length of a String when displayed in the system character set. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}